data.value:
January 22, 2045
It happened a rare thing today. Scientists came to talk with me in the room. According to them with number 1 we are ready for the rest.I do not know what to think ... they will come back soon. They are already preparing us ...
January 25, 2045
It's been two days since scientists come and go. We had not seen so much in a long time. They give us mostly injections. This is for our sake clearly emphasize this. We can soon go to the surface to help. I can not wait to be useful to something ...
January 27, 2045
It's in two days! In two days I will take the test in the company of number 1. We are so impatient!
